articles.title: MotoGP Sepang test: Bagnaia under lap record to lay down marker on final day - Motorsport.com
articles.description: MotoGP world champion Francesco Bagnaia topped the final day of the Sepang pre-season test, as he led four riders into the 1m56s marker.
articles.content: Under a cloudy sky that provided cooler conditions for the start of the track action, the two-time MotoGP world champion's 1m56.682s remained the time to beat throughout the day, with several challen… [+2309 chars]
